	<label>former</label>
	<description>Formers are creatures of living metal created on the basis of hybrid node technologies. Their origins are not known in detail, but the formers are not directly related to the mechanoids.\n\nThanks to their unique hybrid structure, Formers can feel pain and think freely. The Former's heart and brain are completely organic and reside in the Former's head, however, due to their organic origin, they are also susceptible to disease. Formers do not have manipulators and interact with the world using telekinetic abilities generated by the core. The Former Core also allows them to levitate. The former heart has a natural colony of meсhanites, due to which it can perform metabolic functions.\n\nThese hybrid creatures also have innate psi abilities despite limited psychic sensitivity.\n\n&lt;color=#f5ffa2&gt;Note:&lt;/color&gt; This race does not support vanilla implants and limbs, so implants from the mod are required to restore limbs.</description>
